* Properties functionality above class UCharacterProperty
 * but below class CharacterProperties and class UnicodeSet.
 * @hide Only a subset of ICU is exposed in Android

variables.name: inclusions
variables.comment:
* A set of all characters _except_ the second through last characters of
     * certain ranges. These ranges are ranges of characters whose
     * properties are all exactly alike, e.g. CJK Ideographs from
     * U+4E00 to U+9FA5.

methods.name: public static synchronized UnicodeSet getInclusionsForProperty(int prop)
methods.comment: * Returns a mutable UnicodeSet -- do not modify!

methodNames: public static synchronized UnicodeSet getInclusionsForProperty(int prop)
